{"tid":313164,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞啦喂]《氵㸒》(改自junno mak《彳亍》)","createTime":"2017-07-08T06:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T15:14:53.000Z","uid":112643,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6496d7885f7cd74ed461b934d91d982b9e448ea0","tid":313164,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:13:40.000Z","msg":"作詞：周耀輝<br />\n改詞：fing春及一眾連登巴打<br />\n作曲：馮穎琪<br />\n編曲：Jerald<br />\n監製：Jerald<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">波和波之間夾了碌鳩</span>　無數<span style=\"color: red;\">碌鳩</span><br />\n如<span style=\"color: red;\">我插你</span>  換過絲的衣著行入每顆心臟<br />\n天和天之間隔了天荒　地老天荒<br />\n踏出啞的感覺　行入幾多個軀殼<br />\n<br />\n若你說<span style=\"color: red;\">碌鳩插</span>甚麼　<span style=\"color: red;\">閪窿噴</span>甚麼<br />\n只想<span style=\"color: red;\">碌勁插</span>天光<br />\n若你說已到了<span style=\"color: red;\">高潮</span>　太快樂<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">含實我　射左</span>　但我希望<span style=\"color: red;\">插</span>到我<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">很想抱住屌</span>　很想<span style=\"color: red;\">插騾閪</span><br />\n可否跟我沿著甚麼邊走邊看藏著甚麼<br />\n方知一切故事在遊蕩<br />\n很想到無邊搜索　然後與歲月摔角<br />\n為了知生存過不生存過 <br />\n很想<span style=\"color: red;\">用對波包住頭　插過　插過</span><br />\n<br />\n山和海之間永遠蒼蒼　雲雨蒼蒼<br />\n如你信我　望向瘋的孔雀行入赤色的浪<br />\n身和心之間永遠剛剛　眉眼剛剛<br />\n認識新的乾涸　行入浮泥仍在喝<br />\n<br />\n很想唱驪歌　很想探洪荒<br />\n可否跟我沿著甚麼邊走邊看藏著甚麼<br />\n方知一切故事在遊蕩<br />\n很想到無邊搜索　然後與歲月摔角<br />\n善惡多　生命更多　味更多　道更多　路更多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">碌鳩向前隊</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">屎忽向上撓</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">出精</span>的我緩慢站起彳亍走向<span style=\"color: red;\">對波</span><br />\n在我的無邊搜索　然後與歲月摔角<br />\n為了知生存過不生存過<br />\n很想在<span style=\"color: red;\">塊閪崩裂前</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">插過　屌過　含柒靠嘴角</span><br />\n<br />\n拋磚劣改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望大家俾多啲料黎齊齊改好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人肯唱就最perfect池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f02ae21f05ae3b21b80439c29f8935bc2fa4a2","tid":313164,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1de2c9114a8f4ea978e8929aec6f1d838514eca","tid":313164,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:15:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3540d532393e021948486c4c647adfb37ece63ce","tid":313164,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:15:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cdc71472287e7808c1005db9641462a183e2e5","tid":313164,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6c334cdb48538e8b99ae0969ba55167766c11d","tid":313164,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:16:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf65bc1e837dcc62a5423c037423c581f34b97a0","tid":313164,"uid":112643,"